{
  "stem": "12051.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Cracow wouldn't let us in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the closest to Cracow was a city called Wieliczka, where my father's sister lived, by the name of [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And when I arrived there-- she had also a daughter that was a little bit older than I am.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she was very much afraid that the Germans will come in and they will rape everybody.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she told us to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Another cousin of mine that came from Cracow with a baby of four weeks-- and we ran away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went as far as we could, possibly to reach the Russian border.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the Germans caught up with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was-- we had to return.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I returned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CRYING] We had to return.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that time, my parents have arrived already from Bielitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were reunited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also not for a very long time because then my parents moved to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in Cracow, shortly thereafter, they started to put up the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Being that we didn't want to stay in the ghetto, and we were not, so to say, [NON-ENGLISH] to Cracow, we had to move back to Wieliczka.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they would not permit, unless you were a resident of the city, to stay in the city.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You had to move out 30 kilometers out of any big city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we went back to Wieliczka.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we stayed with my aunt and uncle and her children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In [SIGHS] 1940-- this all was a short time, but it was a very cruel time and a very disoriented time for us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, one suitcase.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How much can you get from home?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have as-- what?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My uncle came to pick my parents up with the car.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
